lead_paragraph: England players will be shown video clips of previous clashes against Scotland in the build-up to Friday's World Cup qualifier, including Paul Gascoigne's memorable goal and equally unforgettable celebration at Euro 96.

headline.print_headline: England to Watch Gazza Clip in Build-Up to Scotland Clash
